A shekarun 1980, ya yi aiki a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon don ya ci nasara a kan wani ɗan wasan Amurka mai suna Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama Shugaba na Microsoft Research da shugaban kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
