Taron Trump a West Virginia a tashar YouTube
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara taron da ya yi a Wheeling, West Virginia a yau.
Wannan ne karo na farko na taron Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a jihohin da ya fi so, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tun da yake ba a tabbatar da takararsa na neman kujerar kotun koli ba, Trump yana neman goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar rashin ikon da za su yi wa majalisa bayan zaben da aka yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a West Virginia, kuma a ina za a iya kallon taron a Intanet?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, zai kasance a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018, da karfe 7 na yammacin rana.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kai a kai a tashar YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana game da sauraron da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Bret Kavanaugh a wannan makon, wanda ya zama mai rikitarwa saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i, wanda ya sa a sa ran a jinkirta amincewar majalisar dattijai na mako guda don FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban abin da wannan taron zai yi shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su sake samun ci gaba a lokacin babban zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, a lokacin yakin neman zaben shugaban kasar Trump, an yi amfani da waɗannan majalisun guda biyar don ƙarfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da kuma ƙara rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
"Sauye-sauyen da ake yi a majalisar dokokin Amirka yana da muhimmanci sosai ga shirinsa, saboda haka a lokacin da ake fama da matsi, shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa ƙasashe da yawa", wani wakilin Trump da ba ya son a nada shi ya shaida wa Reuters.
A yau, ana shirin yin taron a Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling, West Virginia MetroNews ta ruwaito cewa masu goyon bayan da ke Ohio da Pennsylvania za su iya halarta, kuma hakan zai jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, inda ya samu sama da kashi 40 cikin dari na maki a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana ƙoƙarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Jam'iyyar Republican daga West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya yi baya a binciken binciken jama'a.
"Maganar cewa shugaban kasa ya zo ya yi masa maraba a cikin binciken jama'a ba shi da kyau ga Morrisey", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar wani rahoto na Reuters.
