HIV/aids: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar 14 cikin 100 na sababbin kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta ce ta samu karuwar yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS da kashi 14 cikin 100.
Jami'an lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne suka sha wahala a ƙasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an yi rahoton kusan sababbin shari'o'i 40,000.
A yawancin sababbin cututtuka, an kamu da cutar ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji a kan abin da ya faru a baya.
A wasu sassa na ƙasar Sin, yawanci, an yi amfani da jinin da aka yi wa kamuwa da cutar ta wajen yaduwar cutar.
Amma, a taron da aka yi a lardin Junan, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV a wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu.
Amma har yanzu, adadin mutanen da ke rayuwa da HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT a kasar Sin.
An yi watsi da jima'i a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma har yanzu ana nuna bambanci ga 'yan LGBT.
Domin har ila yau, ana bin ƙa'idodin 'yan adawa a ƙasar, binciken ya nuna cewa 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mace a lokaci.
