Sabuwar jirgin yakin Jamus da aka sake ajiyewa
A cewar wani rahoto, an yi rahoton cewa, a shekara ta 2014, za a yi amfani da sabon jirgin ruwan da aka yi amfani da shi a cikin rundunar jiragen ruwa na Jamus don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na yakin Cold War, amma saboda lalacewar tsarin da kuma saurin karuwar farashin, ba za a yi amfani da shi ba har zuwa shekara mai zuwa.
A yanzu an yi shirin kawo jirgin ruwa mai suna Rheinland-Pfalz, wanda shi ne babban jirgin ruwa na sabon rukuni na Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa rabin shekara ta 2019, in ji jaridar Die Zeit, inda ta ambata wani wakilin soja.
An yi shirin tura jirgin zuwa rundunar jiragen ruwa a shekara ta 2014, amma an yi wani shiri mai ban sha'awa da ya jawo damuwa bayan an kai shi.
Jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg, da aka ba da umarni a shekara ta 2007, za su maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Ana sa ran za su yi amfani da manyan makamai masu linzami, da wasu makamai masu linzami da kuma wasu fasahohin ɓoyewa kamar su radar, infrared da kuma siginar sauti.
