Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 a filin wasa na Le Golf National a birnin Paris, Faransa, ta hanyar lashe gasar ta Amurka da lambar yabo ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5.
A yanzu dai, Amurka ta yi rashin nasara a kan filayen Turai sau shida a jere kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun tagomashi a lokacin da tawagar da aka kafa ta Danish Captain Thomas Bjorna ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don cin nasara a kan Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa kwallon a cikin ruwa a ramin 16 a wasan Par-3 a farkon bugun sa, wanda ya sa ya ba da wasan ga Francesc Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi haskakawa a cikin dukkan zagaye kuma ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka taɓa samun nasara 5-0-0 tun lokacin da gasar ta fara a cikin nau'i na yanzu a 1979.
Jordan Spieth, dan Amurka, ya ci Thorbjorn Olesen daga Denmark, dan wasan da ya fi kowa daraja a Turai, da maki biyar da hudu.
Dustin Johnson, wanda ya fi kowa daraja a duniya, ya ci nasara da 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda wataƙila shi ne ya buga gasar Ryder a karo na ƙarshe.
Tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup na takwas, Sergio Garcia, dan Spain, ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi nasara a gasar cin kofin duniya, da maki 25.5.
Ba na yawan kuka, amma yau ba zan iya taimakawa kaina ba.
