"Wannan wasa ne na musamman, kuma ina farin cikin taimaka wa", in ji Garcia bayan nasarar da ta samu a Turai.
Wannan takardar ta mika wa ɗan'uwanmu John Ram, wanda ya ci wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods a wasan biyu da ɗaya a ranar Lahadi.
