Woods ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu da ya buga a Faransa, kuma yanzu yana da rikodin Ryder Cup 13-21-3.
Wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki ga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na dukan lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan lakabi 14, daidai bayan Jack Nicklaus.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta yi aiki tuƙuru a duk mako don neman hanyar da ta dace, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas, da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasa a golf a babban matakin a duk lokacin gasar.
Bayan da ya yi mummunan aiki a tawagarsa, sai wani shugaban Amurka ya ce, "Ina alfahari da 'yan wasan nan, sun yi gwagwarmaya".
