Labarin Rashin Ruwa: Taron ruwa a bakin tekun Pinellas, Manatee da Saratoga yana raguwa
Wani rahoto na kwanan nan na Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Daun daji ta Florida (FWC) ya nuna cewa yawan adadin ruwan damfara a yankin Tampa Bay ya ragu.
Hukumar FWC ta ba da rahoton samun ƙarin fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Saratoga, Charlotte da Collier County, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Ƙarshen ruwan Red Tide yana nisan mil 130 daga arewacin yankin Pinellas zuwa kudancin yankin Lee.
Ana ganin raƙuman ruwa ne a kusan mil 10 daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma a ƙananan wurare fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga wani abu mai launin ruwan kasa a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an ruwaito matsakaitan matakan da aka samu a Pinellas County da kuma gabar tekun ta, ƙananan zuwa manyan matakan da aka samu a gabar tekun Hillsborough County, ƙananan zuwa manyan matakan da aka samu a Manatee County, ƙananan zuwa manyan matakan da aka samu a Saratoos County da gabar tekun ta, ƙananan zuwa manyan matakan da aka samu a Charlotte County, ƙananan zuwa manyan matakan da aka samu a Lee County da gabar tekun ta, da ƙananan matakan da aka samu a Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni daga Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da Collier County.
Ba a samu rahoto daga yankin arewa maso yammacin Florida na tashin hankali a makon da ya gabata ba.
